node.text: Stunning work, I just love the framing and the lighting! 🔥

Capturing London’s iconic red buses in the rain. Sometimes, you’ve got to get down low, find those leading lines, and shift your angle to reveal something truly epic. It’s all about exploring new viewpoints to turn ordinary shots into extraordinary ones.

A quick Breakdown to how I edit in Lightroom / photoshop , let me know if you wished to see more like this 🙌🏼
